# Installation instructions
For now you will have to install using `devtools::install_github("rmhogervorst/PACKAGENAME")`

Installation via cran with : install_packages(NAMEOFPACKAGE)




# Contact and contributing
I'm always looking for ways to improve my work. You can help me out with many things. Even small ones like typos or unclear
documentation. Open source is community work, I appreciate everyone's help. 

Contact me directly through mail: ( hogervorst.rm [at] gmail [dot] com ), use the  [issue tracker](https://github.com/RMHogervorst/PACKAGENAME/issues), fork me and/or submit a pull request.

If you are new to open source development or github, or you want more details about contributing, I made a [seperate page for that](contributing.md)
I may even have [beginner](https://github.com/RMHogervorst/PACKAGE/issues?q=is%3Aopen+is%3Aissue+label%3A%22beginner%22) issues that you can solve. 

# Support:
If you are having issues you can open a new issue in the issue tracker. I would like to know the following things: 

- what did you want to do?
- what happened (for instance: error message came on your screen)
- what do you think is the cause of the problem?

I will try to answer within 1 week, if you haven't heard from me, please email me.


